\c 13
\s Kunamata kwenhema
\p
\v 1 Kana kukabva muporofita kana muroti wehope\x + Zek. 10.2.\x* pakati pako, ndokukupa chiratidzo kana chishamiso\x + Mat. 7.22,23. 24.24. 2 VaTes. 2.9,11. Zvak. 13.14.\x*,
\v 2 zvino icho chiratidzo kana chishamiso chikaitika chaakataura kwauri achiti: Ngatitevere vamwe vamwari vausina kuziva uye ngativashumire\x + 18.22. Jer. 28.9.\x*;
\v 3 usateerera kumashoko emuporofita uyo kana kumuroti wehope uyo, nokuti Jehovha Mwari wenyu anokuidzai, kuti azive kuti munomuda here Jehovha Mwari wenyu nemoyo wenyu wose uye nemweya wenyu wose\x + 8.2.\x*.
\v 4 Jehovha Mwari wenyu muchamutevera, uye muchatya iye, nemirairo yake muchachengeta, uye inzwi rake teererai, uye muchashumira iye\x + 2 Madz. 23.3. 2 Makor. 34.31.\x*, nekunamata iye\x + 10.20.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino muporofita uyo kana muroti wehope uyo ngaaurawe; nokuti wakataura ku\add ku\add*tsausa kubva pana Jehovha Mwari wenyu wakakubudisai kubva panyika yeEgipita, nekukudzikunurai kubva muimba yeuranda\x + 18.20. Jer. 14.15. Zek. 13.3.\x*, kukutinhirai kunze kwenzira Jehovha Mwari wako yaakakuraira kufamba mairi\x + 13.5,10. 2 Madz. 17.21.\x*. Saizvozvo uchabvisa kuipa kubva pakati pako\x + 17.7,12. 19.19. 21.21. 22.21,22,24. 24.7. 1 VaKori. 5.13.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Kana munin'ina kana mukoma wako, mwanakomana wamai vako, kana mwanakomana wako\x + 17.2.\x*, kana mwanasikana wako, kana mukadzi wepachifuva chako, kana shamwari\x + 28.54,56. Mik. 7.5.\x* yako yakaita semweya wako, akakukwezva pakavanda achiti: Ngatiende tinoshumira vamwe vamwari vausina kuziva iwe kana madzibaba ako\x + 1 Sam. 18.1,3. 20.17.\x*,
\v 7 chavamwari vevanhu vakakupoteredzai, vari pedo newe kana kure newe, kubva pane rumwe rutivi rwenyika kusvika kune rumwe rutivi rwenyika\x + 6.14.\x*.
\v 8 Usamutendera kana kuteerera kwaari\x + Zvir. 1.10.\x*; ziso rako risamunzwira tsitsi, uye usamurega, kana kumuvanza\x + 7.16.\x*;
\v 9 asi uchamuuraya zvirokwazvo; ruoko rwako rwuchava rwekutanga kumuuraya, zvino pashure ruoko rwevanhu vose\x + 17.7.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino uchamutaka nemabwe kuti afe\x + 17.5.\x*, nokuti watsvaka kukutinhira kure naJehovha Mwari wako, iye wakakubudisa panyika yeEgipita paimba yeuranda\x + 13.5,10; 2 Madz. 17.21.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino Israeri wose achazvinzwa, ndokutya, uye haangaitizve seichi chinhu chakaipa pakati pako\x + 17.13. 19.20.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Kana ukanzwa kune rimwe remaguta ako Jehovha Mwari wako aanokupa kugaramo kuchinzi\x + Josh. 22.11.\x*:
\v 13 Varume, vana vaBheriari, vanobuda kubva pakati pako, uye vasundidzira vagari veguta ravo vachiti: Handei tinoshumira vamwe vamwari vamusina kuziva;
\v 14 zvino uchatsvaka, ndokutsvakisisa, ndokubvunza zvakanaka; tarira, kana chiri chokwadi, chinhu icho ndechechokwadi, chinyangadzo ichi chakaitwa pakati pako\x + 17.4. 19.18.\x*,
\v 15 ucharova kwazvo vagari veguta iro nekwakapinza kwemunondo, uchiriparadza chose, nechose chiri mariri, nezvipfuwo zvaro, nekwakapinza kwemunondo\x + Eki. 22.20. Josh. 6.17,21.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino uchaunganidza chakapambiwa charo chose pakati pemugwagwa waro, uye uchapisa guta nemoto nechakapambiwa charo chose zvachose, kuna Jehovha Mwari wako\x + Josh. 6.24.\x*; zvino richava dutu rinhi narinhi; haringavakwizve\x + Josh. 8.28. Jer. 49.2.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino pasanamatira paruoko rwako chimwe chezvakatukwa, kuti Jehovha adzoke pakupfuta kwekutsamwa kwake, uye akupe ngoni, agokunzwira tsitsi, nekukuwanza\x + Josh. 7.26.\x*, sezvaakapikira madzibaba ako\x + Gen.. 22.16,17. Gen.. 50.24.\x*;
\v 18 kana ukateerera kuinzwi raJehovha Mwari wako, kuchengeta mirairo yake yose yandinokuraira nhasi, kuita zvakarurama pameso aJehovha Mwari wako\x + 12.25,28.\x*.